ttps://kenrockwell.com/tech/comparisons/iphone-vs-full-frame-bokeh.htm\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">depth of field</a> and bokeh simulation while comparing it to a full-frame DSLR.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p> 	 <strong>Summary:</strong>\n The iPhone XS offers significant camera improvement over last year\'s \niPhone X. However, the Samsung devices continue to hold their own. \nDepending on what you are photographing, either phone may give superior \nresults to the other, and you cannot go wrong either way.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p> 	 <strong>Winner:</strong> Tie</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->', 'Samsung vs. Apple Camera Test', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '32-revision-v1', '', '', '2019-02-12 15:32:34', '2019-02-12 15:32:34', '', 32, 'http://localhost/Techthirstie/index.php/2019/02/12/32-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
